** Story**

Once upon a time, in a forest, there lives a monkey who resided on the berry tree, which was on the bank of the river.
In the same forest there lived a crocodile and his wife.
One day, crocodile came to the bank of the river and rested under the tree.
The kind hearted monkey offered him some fruits. The crocodile came back the next day and they became good friends.


One day monkey sent some fruits for crocodile's wife. She ate the fruits but wanted to break friendship of his husband and monkey.
So she asked him to bring the heart of the monkey, Crocodile not wanted to do it but she acted that she is ill and can be cured only by eating monkeys heart.


*** FLip Story**
Monkey is villian and crocodile and crocodile's wife r good